進其運作，提請人們注意其工作中可能阻撓或妨礙促進、保護和實現人權和基本自由的任何方面&rdquo;；也與中國新權力集團一再宣稱的&ldquo;依法治國&rdquo;與&ldquo;依憲治國&rdquo;相背離。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寫文果個訓左幾耐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:36:24.000Z","msg":"笑左！"},{"pid":"bcd531f1447a4e4b84803c54c6ed3e158d217c50","tid":717477,"uid":18912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/goal.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5272447141a0b9eff3e38e2fcaf6414d132b0a","tid":717477,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"鬼打鬼最好睇 <br />\n但如果一班理論上中國民間最有戰鬥力嘅人，以武力抗爭都係被徹底收皮的話，未來抗爭成功既希望更微薄"},{"pid":"6444dd13f402f7fd61f44489e7bc1653e8fc75ec","tid":717477,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"882d1a2eac4dbe34d29e66f3cebb43b42f4f7f72","tid":717477,"uid":30169,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/181622_74e684192175dd7abcc12cbdc1a13073.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F181622_74e684192175dd7abcc12cbdc1a13073.png&h=55557c58&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/181622_29f88ec4870297def4ac53ee452574f8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F181622_29f88ec4870297def4ac53ee452574f8.png&h=7933635e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"香港代表"},{"pid":"c548e0af6cc6f4837806a9eb132e6d9208cc843d","tid":717477,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c5272447141a0b9eff3e38e2fcaf6414d132b0a","tid":717477,"uid":63482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T10:44:14.000Z","msg":"鬼打鬼最好睇 <br />\n但如果一班理論上中國民間最有戰鬥力嘅人，以武力抗爭都係被徹底收皮的話，未來抗爭成功既希望更微薄"},"citedBy":0,